content:
**Exploring the miscommunication**

Okay, looking into this! It seems the miscommunication happened because the instructions were a bit unclear on role demarcation—since ChatGPT was responding to the instructions, I mistakenly focused on addressing Gemini rather than helping with the integration process. There might have been a mix-up between the instructions due to having two sets of communication goals, one for Gemini and one for helping Jesse. To avoid this in the future, a clearer distinction in the instructions would help.
